 the imagination, it is definitely a very simple game, there are no diplomacy, no research, then you probably think this just a crap game, it is not! the game is incredibly good and it is well made and nicely polished and the sounds are like from heaven, so then you might wonder why is it so good even when it apear so thin? the game is good at ocupying you to strategize how to beat the enemy, it is good to let you experience the kind of gameplay of games like Sins without the need to do a lot of research before you attack, you just dive right into it. go buy it now! it's well worth the full price."
